  "code": "%% Sequence Diagram – Issue Document with Automated Backup & Opportunistic Cloud Sync\n%% Actors: Secretary (Logistics_DeliveryRoute), System services; aligns to Option B schema\n\nsequenceDiagram\n\tautonumber\n\tactor Secretary\n\tparticipant UI as User Interface\n\tparticipant Auth as AuthService\n\tparticipant Iss as IssuanceService\n\tparticipant PDF as PdfService\n\tparticipant FS as FileSystem\n\tparticipant Repo as DB/Repository\n\tparticipant Bkp as BackupService\n\tparticipant Cloud as CloudSyncService\n\n\tSecretary->>UI: Login(Logistics_StockLevel)\n\tUI->>Auth: authenticate(Logistics_FleetManagement)\n\tAuth-->>UI: auth result\n\tUI-->>Secretary: login success\n\n\tNote over Secretary,UI: Start issuance\n\tSecretary->>UI: Enter requester details, type, purpose\n\tUI->>Iss: createIssuance(Logistics_DeliveryRoute)\n\tIss->>PDF: generate(Logistics_FleetManagement)\n\tPDF-->>Iss: PDF bytes/path\n\tIss->>FS: save PDF artifact\n\tFS-->>Iss: path + fileHash\n\tIss->>Repo: save IssuanceRecord + Artifact(Logistics_DeliveryRoute)\n\tRepo-->>Iss: confirm IDs\n\tIss-->>UI: issuance created + artifact path\n\tUI-->>Secretary: show preview/print\n\n\tUI->>Bkp: queueLocal(Logistics_StockLevel)\n\tBkp->>FS: copy to backup location\n\tFS-->>Bkp: copy OK\n\tBkp->>Repo: record BackupLog(Logistics_FleetManagement)\n\tRepo-->>Bkp: logged\n\tBkp->>Cloud: upload(Logistics_FleetManagement)  \n\tNote over Cloud: If offline, enqueue and retry when online\n\tCloud-->>Bkp: result (Logistics_DeliveryRoute)\n\tBkp->>Repo: update BackupLog + Artifact.syncStatus\n\tRepo-->>Bkp: updated\n\tBkp-->>UI: backup status / alerts\n\tUI-->>Secretary: notify backup/cloud status\n\n\tNote over Secretary,Cloud: End of issuance flow\n",
